<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <%= analytics_init if GoogleAnalytics.valid_tracker? %>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <title>DevOps On Demand - Hire freelance AWS, Azure, & Google Cloud engineers from around the world.</title>
